title: Slicer Ninja is launching soon on kickstarter! Donâ€™t miss out! #3dprinter #3dprinted  #trending
description:
Sign up for free here:  http://kickstarter.com/projects/slicerninja/slicer-ninja-ai-3d-print-file-optimizer

What Is Slicer Ninja?

Slicer Ninja is a web-based tool designed to take the guesswork out of slicer settings.

Instead of digging through menus, forums, and trial-and-error prints, Slicer Ninja analyzes your model, your printer, and your filament, then recommends optimized slicer settings automatically. The goal is simple: better prints, less waste, and less time spent fighting your slicer.

You upload a model, select your printer and material, and Slicer Ninja helps optimize things like orientation, layer height, walls, infill, flow, and speedâ€”based on real-world printing logic, not generic presets. Itâ€™s built to work with your existing slicer, not replace it.

Whether youâ€™re new to 3D printing or youâ€™ve been doing this for years, Slicer Ninja is meant to save time, reduce failed prints, and help you get consistent results without overthinking every setting.
